title: LoLPatcher
body: 000004.400|  ERROR| Riot::RADS::Patching::RetrieveReleaseListing: C:/jenkins/workspace/rads-code-win-release/code/Solutions/RiotRADS/Source/RADS/Patching/Networking/ClientServer/RemoteFileServerCommon.cpp(63): Failed to create version number from release listing entry "

replies.body: It looks like your OS may be blocking the patcher from reading and writing files.  I recommend going over the steps in our [Permissions ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)guide to get this resolved.  Please let me know if you have any issues after!
